description:
This is a 25 minute workout called '20 MIN EXPRESS PILATES WORKOUT || Power Pilates For Energy (Moderate/Intermediate)' from the channel Move With Nicole.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Pilates.
It's suitable for Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Masterclass Workout and The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.
